  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>The Beausite Park Hotel and Spa is on a half board basis. </p>
<p>Each morning you can fuel up for the day with a varied buffet breakfast with daily hot options, and a live cooking station for egg dishes. On your departure day, a packed breakfast is available - Please order at reception the day before. </p>
<p>When you return from a day on the mountain, enjoy a four course evening meal with a choice of main course often including a meat, vegetarian and fish option. Please note that if the starter and soup is not vegetarian, there is an alternative menu with appropriate choices - Please note that this menu does not change. An <span>an à la carte menu is available (pay locally). </span></p>
<p>Christmas and New Year dinners are included.</p>
<p> </p>]]></cateringDescription>
