  <locationDescription><![CDATA[<p>The hotel is in a slightly elevated position with excellent views over the village and towards the Jungfrau region.</p>
<p>The Beausite Park Hotel and Spa is just a 5 minutes' walk (500m) to the village centre and the Männlichen cable-car for access to the 'Männlichen -Kleine Scheidegg' ski area. Alternatively, you can ski down via the nursery slopes, which start in front of the hotel (weather conditions permitting).</p>]]></locationDescription>
