  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Forest Side Twin Rooms </strong>are around 25m² sleeping two people with Austrian twin beds. These rooms tend to be at the rear of the hotel, with a forest view. These rooms are available for single use on request, please give our Reservations team a call if you'd like to book.</p>
<p><strong>Jungfrau View Twin Rooms </strong>are around 25m² sleeping two people with Austrian twin beds. These rooms are located at the front side of the hotel, and have a balcony with views of the Jungfrau and surrounding mountains. </p>
<p><strong>Junior Suites</strong> are more spacious at around 32m² sleeping two people.  These rooms have a balcony with views of the Jungfrau and surrounding mountains. These rooms are on request, please give our Reservations team a call if you'd like to book.</p>
<p> </p>
<p><strong>Room Facilities</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Satellite TV</li>
<li>Free Wi-Fi</li>
<li>Safe</li>
<li>Mini fridge</li>
<li>Tea and coffee facilities</li>
<li>Safe</li>
<li>Bathrobes</li>
<li>Bath with showerhead attachment </li>
<li>Iron, adapters and charging cables are available on request (refundable deposit required)</li>
</ul>]]></roomsDescription>
